{"data":[{"date":"07:26 18/08","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tu-bolton-den-juventus-b-hanh-trinh-su-nghiep-15-nam-cua-cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m ng\u00e0y Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Bolton Wanderers, di\u1ec7n ki\u1ebfn 67.647 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Old Trafford. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n sao m\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i th\u00e2n quen ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua\u2026</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Manchester...</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sir Alex Ferguson \u0111ang d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, g\u00e3 trai tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 18 thay th\u1ebf Nicky Butt khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o b\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n b\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 12,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 mang tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng, k\u1ebf th\u1eeba c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Beckham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bolton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m (16/08/2003)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7y nh\u1eb3ng, m\u1eb7t l\u1ea5m t\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ebb b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng hay ho g\u00ec m\u1ea5y. M\u1ed9t m\u00e1i t\u00f3c t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u r\u1ed1i b\u1eddi, b\u00f9 x\u00f9 nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5 qu\u1ea1, b\u00f3ng nh\u1eaby nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u nh\u1edbt v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9y light b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f4i ba s\u1ee3i m\u00ec spaghetti th\u1eeba l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u0129a \u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee5c t\u00ecm v\u00e0 xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c video tr\u00ean Youtube v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League 2003/04 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn con s\u1ed1 tri\u1ec7u view, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghe th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 c\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed3ng ca mang h\u00e0m \u00fd m\u1ec9a mai, ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Bolton r\u1ed3i: <strong><em>&ldquo;M\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng n\u00e0o?&rdquo;</em></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/ronaldo-11.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus: C\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o cho c\u1ea3 Serie A</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u01b0 c\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o, b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i thay c\u1ee7a Serie A trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Nicky Hunt ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1eadu nh\u00f3c qu\u00ea m\u00f9a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea3 xung h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9t kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf Old Trafford, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 g\u00e2y ra \u1edf hai b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cristiano mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00e1i v\u1ed7 m\u1eb7t kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roy Keane. C\u00f3 anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Man Utd ghi th\u00eam ba b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Cristiano-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-voi-lang-que-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bolton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m (16/08/2003)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Sam Allardyce c\u0169ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 b\u1edbt ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian l\u1eafng nghe chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Mario Jardel, t\u00e2n binh Bolton c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Sporting Lisbon, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0ng h\u00f3a ra v\u00f4 danh l\u1ea1 ho\u1eafc kia, v\u1edbi g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 non cho\u1eb9t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chia tay Bolton n\u0103m 2010, Hunt lang b\u1ea1t qua 11 CLB tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i \u1edf Notts County. M\u00f9ng 10 th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y n\u0103m nay, anh ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1edbi Crewe Alexandra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng t\u01b0 kh\u00e1c, sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd Juventus th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha Real Madrid, gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Cristiano-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-voi-lang-que-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">... \u0111\u1ebfn mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh Villar Perosa</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 r\u01b0\u1ee1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG c\u00f9ng h\u00e0nh trang 5 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng hay s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u V\u0110QG c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Champions League t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, CR7 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Old Trafford hay Santiago de Bernabeu tr\u00e1ng l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 huy\u00ean n\u00e1o. Villar Perosa l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli tr\u1ecb v\u00ec Juventus, n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i n\u00f4i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Villar Perosa Juventus\" title=\"Villar Perosa Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/55.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u00e0ng Villar Perosa \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u1eafc n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd - Qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli tr\u1ecb v\u00ec Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">63 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, ng\u00f4i l\u00e0ng b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh n\u1eb1m c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 ph\u1ee7 Turin 50km v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00e2y nam n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u00e0n giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi Juventus Primavera.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n y\u00ean b\u00ecnh trong n\u0103m nay, v\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao. \u00d4 t\u00f4 r\u1ed3ng r\u1eafn n\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eadu ngo\u00e0i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n t\u1eeb 6 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n. V\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n h\u1ebft s\u1ea1ch trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft. 5000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n 1000 so v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 d\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh \u1edf Villar Perosa, quy t\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-0 cho c\u00e1c anh l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Massmiliano Allegri. D\u00f9 g\u00ec, \u0111\u00e1m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tu\u1ed5i teen kia c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Diego Godin \u1edf Sochi h\u01a1n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u00e0y Uruguay lo\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/23.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: Ng\u00e0y si\u00eau sao ra m\u1eaft \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 giao l\u01b0u v\u00e0 k\u00fd t\u1eb7ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb&hellip; l\u1ed9t s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfc qu\u1ea7n l\u00f3t m\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding:10px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kho\u1ea3ng kh\u1eafc vinh quang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n thi\u00eang li\u00eang v\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i.</em></div>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gigi Buffon, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Bianconeri gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Paris Saint-Germain</em></span></td>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/river.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: Ng\u00e0y si\u00eau sao ra m\u1eaft \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Verona, Juventus &ldquo;l\u1edbn&rdquo; ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean vai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 ra l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u: <em>&ldquo;N\u0103m nay, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.&rdquo;</em> Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Serie A hay Coppa Italia, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh h\u01a1n hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft bu\u1ed3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb Bolton \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus B, t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Manchester \u0111\u1ebfn mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh Villar Perosa, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 15 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1eadu cho si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi cho di s\u1ea3n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo Juventus\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/tu-bolton-den-juventus-b-hanh-trinh-su-nghiep-15-nam-cua-cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng Champions League cho B\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7m Gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in;\"><strong><em>* Theo Telegraph</em></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus: C\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o cho c\u1ea3 Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-thu-loi-tu-cristiano-ronaldo-khong-nhieu-nhu-nguoi-ta-van-nghi-176-192158.html\">Juventus thu l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/tu-juventus-den-ac-milan-ke-hoach-tro-ve-thoi-hoang-kim-cua-serie-a-176-194193.html\">T\u1eeb Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan: K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5613","checkdouble":"194602"},{"date":"08:33 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-monaco-vs-lille-01h00-ngay-198-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco vs Lille l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Monaco-vs-Lille.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Monaco vs Lille</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Monaco vs Lille: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 x\u00e9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n y\u1ebfu \u0111i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc song Monaco v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Ligue 1 2018/19 khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nantes. V\u00f2ng 2 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Leonardo Jardim c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Louis II. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Lille, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 4 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ligue 1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t m\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, Monaco \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Lille v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd cps chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng n\u1eefa. Song k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Monaco \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nantes \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau khi chia tay HLV Ranieri. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 chia tay kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Fabinho, Moutinho hay Lemar. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn, HLV Jardim ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 1 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Golovin nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLille s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9m Monaco nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Rennes \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Christophe Galtier ch\u1ec9 thua 1/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00eam nay gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang t\u1edbi k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. 5 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Monaco to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Lille g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ligue 1.<br>\r\n- 5 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Monaco: V\u1eafng Aleksandr Golovin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng), Djibril Sidibe v\u00e0 Danijel Subasic; Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Adama Traore v\u00e0 Almamy Toure c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Lille: V\u1eafng Luiz Araujo (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5612","checkdouble":"194716"},{"date":"08:18 18/08","title":"Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng Arsenal thua \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n HLV Emery, qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng v\u1edbi sang ch\u1ecdc ngo\u00e1y Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Shkodran Mustafi l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Arsene Wenger mang v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Valencia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf Emirates, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Unai Emery, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi Mustafi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Sokratis \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1edd phong c\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n s\u00e1t sao h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u mang h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf Stamford Bridge:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cEmery n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00ec cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1edfi anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m g\u00ec khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi HLV. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cTr\u1eadn thua Man City th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Chelsea ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng v\u1eady. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, tr\u00e1i ng\u1ecdt sau c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5611","checkdouble":"194710"},{"date":"07:32 18/08","title":"HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger, HLV Unai Emery m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Manchester City v\u00e0 Chelsea, &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Mesut Ozil. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. M\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau, c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, Ozil c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10, ho\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng&quot; - Unai Emery nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m th\u1ebf trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ozil l\u00e0m g\u00ec&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Arsenal vs Chelsea s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mesut Ozil:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-nhan-chi-trich-tham-te-tu-huyen-thoai-arsenal-172-194464.html\">Ozil nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/neuer-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-va-quyet-dinh-giai-nghe-192-192607.html\">Neuer: &ldquo;Ozil c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/a-172-192592.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft &ldquo;l\u00e0m m\u00e0u&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/quoc-te/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil-290-192417.html\">C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-p2-389-192316.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly (P2)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-psg-emery-het-loi-ca-ngoi-ozil-172-192233.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t PSG, Emery h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Ozil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5610","checkdouble":"194714"},{"date":"08:53 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8): \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Brigde v\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt ni\u1ec1m tin cho Arsenal, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n trong khi Maurizio Sarri c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n.</h2><h2>Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u00e0nh London m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi xa l\u1ea1 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u00f2n Arsenal th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 l\u00e2u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 nhau \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery\" title=\"HLV Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/chiu-ap-luc-chi-trich-emery-van-quyet-khong-thay-doi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft thi\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Maurizio Sarri kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n v\u1edbi Chelsea b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u00f4ng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhanh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, Unai Emery th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man City th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi. Ch\u00ednh Sarri c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Sarri v\u00e0 Emery ai t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u1ec9 qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/sarri-hua-hen-giup-chelsea-choi-tot-trong-3-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Sarri c\u00f9ng t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ef1c quan nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri v\u00e0 Emery ch\u1ee9ng minh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t, Sarri \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n khi Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh trong khi Emery sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn &quot;Arsenal c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ai cao tay h\u01a1n?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u1edfi khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. Trong tr\u1eadn thua Man City, c\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1t khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung n\u1eefa trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, Jorginho (Chelsea) v\u00e0 Guendouzi (Arsenal) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Chelsea vs Arsenal\" title=\"Preview Chelsea vs Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal - nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Emery tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u1ec3 Guendouzi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. \u0110\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge, Torreira nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u1ea5m l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea khi \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Jorginho \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Kante.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tung c\u1eb7p trung phong Lacazette - Aubameyang ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri khi c\u1ea3 ba l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pedro v\u00e0 Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1eeb bi\u00ean b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9. Trong tr\u1eadn thua Man City, hai c\u00e1nh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Arsenal khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Sarri s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch khai th\u00e1c khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso v\u00e0 Azpilicueta.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Chelsea th\u1eafng 5 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal t\u1ea1i Premier League, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 4 trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Stamford Bridge hai l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal ch\u01b0a gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong ba tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1/1924.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal ch\u01b0a thua hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 1992-93 (thua Norwich v\u00e0 Blackburn).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea: Marco van Ginkel, Isaiah Brown, Cesc Fabregas ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Mateo Kovacic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal: Sead Kolasinac, Laurent Koscielny, Ainsley Maitland-Niles, Carl Jenkinson ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Nacho Monreal , Danny Welbeck ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chelsea (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Kepa - 28.Azpilicueta, 2.Rudiger, 30.David Luiz, 3.M.Alonso - 7.Kante, 5.Jorginho, 12.Loftus Cheek - 11.Pedro, 29.Morata, 10.Hazard</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal (4-3-1-2):</strong> 1.Cech - 2.Bellerin, 20.Mustafi, 5.Sokratis, 12.Lichtsteiner - 8.Ramsey, 11.Torreira, 29.Guendouzi - 10. Ozil - 9.Lacazette, 14.Aubameyang</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Chelsea 2-0 Arsenal<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen-172-194710.html\">Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chiu-ap-luc-chi-trich-emery-van-quyet-khong-thay-doi-arsenal-172-194709.html\">Ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, Emery v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-joel-campbell-172-194700.html\">Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hazard-172-194702.html\">HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-thiet-quan-cho-tran-derby-gap-arsenal-172-194699.html\">Chelsea thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n cho tr\u1eadn derby g\u1eb7p Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quyet-dinh-ve-huu-non-tren-dtqg-sao-chelsea-tu-hai-chinh-minh-172-194695.html\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 h\u01b0u non tr\u00ean \u0110TQG, sao Chelsea t\u1ef1 h\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5609","checkdouble":"194717"},{"date":"18:15 17/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/8/22/chinh-thuc-juve-chia-tay-marchisio-sau-25-nam-gan-bo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Claudio Marchisio \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Juventus sau khi hai b\u00ean th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t h\u1ee7y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marchisio b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Juventus v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2006/07, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u201cL\u00e3o b\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i \u1edf Serie B v\u00ec v\u1ee5 scandal Calciopoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarchisio d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Empoli theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Sau n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Turin v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Juve. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 389 l\u1ea7n, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 37 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/22/chinh-thuc-juve-chia-tay-marchisio-sau-25-nam-gan-bo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarchisio gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Scudetto \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/12. Anh \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 l\u1ea7n c\u00f9ng Juventus. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Marchisio c\u00f2n c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf Coppa Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Marchisio \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef th\u1eadp m\u00e0 anh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4/2016 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Juventus Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cH\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Claudio Marchisio \u1edf Juventus sau khi hai b\u00ean th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t h\u1ee7y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d, th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 Juve cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn, m\u1ed7i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i danh hi\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 thu\u1edf b\u00e9 c\u1ee7a Marchisio l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt ra l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Marchisio. Theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, ng\u00e0y qua ng\u00e0y, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Bianconeri \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ea3y sinh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Marchisio, ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u vinh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u vui v\u1ebb theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0o m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u00f2n m\u00e0u \u00e1o s\u1ecdc tr\u1eafng \u0111en s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u1edf b\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Claudio! Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 6 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB Serie A. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Marchisio c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/tu-bolton-den-juventus-o-lang-que-villar-perosa-hanh-trinh-su-nghiep-15-nam-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-176-194602.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus-327-194582.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5608","checkdouble":"194689"},{"date":"22:59 17/08","title":"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/ro-tin-que-ngoc-hai-se-roi-slna-de-vao-nam-thi-dau-voi-muc-lot-tay-cuc-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd chia tay SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. </h2><h2>Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB TP.HCM?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t ta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t ta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/que-ngoc-hai-noi-ve-ban-quyen-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd chia tay SLNA sau khi V-League 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB SLNA m\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB TP.HCM v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gia h\u1ea1n m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc \u1edf l\u1ea1i SLNA v\u00ec anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y CLB TP.HCM \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB TP.HCM v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 l\u00f3t tay 8 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng/n\u0103m. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB TP.HCM kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, song n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 \u201cchuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1eadt\u201d khi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn s\u01a1 b\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y TP.HCM \u0111ang \u1edf nh\u00f3m x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i BXH v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Miura gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5607","checkdouble":"194705"},{"date":"23:27 17/08","title":"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Malaysia?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh \u1edf th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho t\u1ea5 HCV t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean, &nbsp;\u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a HLV Kim Hak-Bum l\u1ea1i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2 chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa h\u1ed5 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c1&rdquo;. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/AEN20180730005600315_01_i.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kim Hak-Bum nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &quot;H\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan trong c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1960 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 l\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p t\u1ea5p. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ebd ra t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng C\u0110V H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. HLV Kim Hak-Bum c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i do thua k\u00e9m Malaysia v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. N\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng F. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam' \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5606","checkdouble":"194708"},{"date":"00:08 18/08","title":"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i 17/8 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E, \u0110T Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kyrgyzstan b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/Dieu-gi-giup-U23-Viet-Nam-dang-choi-an-tuong-o-U23-chau-A-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y,\u00a0Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m Malaysia 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Malaysia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp sau do thua th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau, Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u2018c\u00f2n gi\u00fap\u2019 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u1ebfu H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau. Song v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Malaysia n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD bang E\" title=\"ASIAD b\u1ea3ng E\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o tay Malaysia \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, th\u00ec c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng x\u1ea3y ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Malaysia. Khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD\" title=\"ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/VN-HQ.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/thua sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Vi\u1ec7t Nam di\u1ec5n ra s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n l\u00e0: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Malaysia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu 1 trong 4 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra th\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia-168-194708.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia-168-194708.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Malaysia?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh \u1edf th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5605","checkdouble":"194711"},{"date":"19:24 17/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8: C\u1ef1u sao PSG khuy\u00ean Neymar t\u1edbi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-178-cuu-sao-psg-khuyen-neymar-toi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8.</h2><h2>C\u1ef1u sao PSG khuy\u00ean Neymar t\u1edbi Real\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 178 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 178 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-178-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8: Berchiche khuy\u00ean Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Neymar trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG l\u00e0 Yuri Berchiche kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid. Ch\u00ednh Yuri c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn La Liga \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Athletic Bilbao h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi La Liga trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AS v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 thay Ronaldo. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Timo Werner, Rodrigo v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Harry Kane v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u1ed5n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ebb h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<h2>Bacca gia nh\u1eadp Villarreal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Villarreal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Carlos Bacca t\u1eeb AC Milan. Theo th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai b\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Samu Castillejo s\u1ebd ra \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Bacca k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Villarreal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 4 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<h2>Celtic chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Celtic \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Daniel Arzani c\u1ee7a Man City v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. Arzani \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Australia nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Citizens. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Melbourne City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<h2>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Paul Mitchell</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Paul Mitchell c\u1ee7a Red Bull Leipzig \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng Mitchell ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Dele Alli hay Alderweireld. Dan Ashworth, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU.</div>\r\n<h2>Klavan s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Italia trong h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd k\u1ebft gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-178-barca-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-hau-ve-tiem-nang-184-194638.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8: Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-168-fred-tiet-lo-ly-do-gia-nhap-mu-184-194627.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/8: Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5604","checkdouble":"194694"},{"date":"21:11 17/08","title":"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Neymar s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/ban-than-tiet-lo-neymar-se-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yuri Berchiche, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf Paris Saint-Germain, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 sau v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro sang Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm ra \u0111i trong nay mai.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb PSG t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb PSG t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/ban-than-tiet-lo-neymar-se-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb PSG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, khi Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u0169 Barcelona. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Yuri Berchiche tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n s\u1ebd s\u1edbm x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Neymar \u1edf C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Athletic Bilbao:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Neymar s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kho\u00e1c l\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o s\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ecf xanh n\u1eefa, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 s\u1eafc tr\u1eafng. Neymar t\u1eebng c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Barcelona, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh Real Madrid m\u1edbi l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf PSG v\u00e0 th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9, chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi nhau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Neymar ngay tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 CLB v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e1c b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Brazil. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Neymar kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, trong khi Los Blancos d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch n\u1ed5 qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5603","checkdouble":"194697"},{"date":"23:25 17/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/27/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Malcom kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa khi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh si\u00eau sao Leo Messi v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ghi b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean tranh c\u00fap Joan Gamper</span> (<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edb s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp vi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barcelona) n\u0103m nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Malcom, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i b\u1edfi m\u00e0n l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Roma.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/malcom-toi-luon-muon-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c Cules ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Malcom ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Leo Messi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e2n th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Barca sau khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 21: \u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou, v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c th\u1eadt r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Barcelona s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Deportivo Alaves.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5602","checkdouble":"194707"},{"date":"22:12 17/08","title":"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9. Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y Hazard theo ch\u00e2n anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Goal cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/HLV-Sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hazard r\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong 10 ng\u00e0y qua. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield 3-0 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, Cesc Fabregas s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cFabregas \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea3\u201d, HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Fabregas. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng \u1edf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3. Fabregas kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194687.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi-172-194639.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5601","checkdouble":"194702"}]}